Package: karaage3
Architecture: all
Homepage: https://github.com/Karaage-Cluster/karaage
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python, debconf, python-matplotlib (>= 0.98), python-django (>= 1.5), python-alogger (>= 2.0), python-tldap (>= 0.2.9), python-django-xmlrpc (>= 0.1), python-django-south (>= 0.7), django-simple-captcha, python-ajax-select (>= 1.3.3), python-django-celery
Recommends: karaage3-celery, python-cracklib
Breaks: karaage (<< 3.0.0), karaage-admin (<< 3.0.0), karaage-registration (<< 3.0.0), karaage-common (<< 1.1.3-4)
Replaces: karaage (<< 3.0.0)
Description: Collection of Django apps to manage a cluster
 Features
 .
  Can store user information and/or posix account information in LDAP
  Admin portal for cluster administrators
  User portal for cluster account holders
  Usage portal, special portal just displaying usage information
  Email notification
  Auto account creation - Allow project leaders to manager their users 
 .
 Modules
 .
  people - Manage people and institutes
  project - Manage projects
  usage - displays usage statistics generated from cluster data
  software - Manage software licenses and agreements
  machines - Manage clusters and cluster user accounts
  projectreports - create surveys for project leaders to fill out 

Package: karaage3-celery
Architecture: all
Homepage: https://github.com/Karaage-Cluster/karaage
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, karaage3-admin
Recommends: rabbitmq-server
Description: Celery server for karaage
 Features
 .
  Can store user information and/or posix account information in LDAP
  Admin portal for cluster administrators
  User portal for cluster account holders
  Usage portal, special portal just displaying usage information
  Email notification
  Auto account creation - Allow project leaders to manager their users 
 .
 This package starts the celery server required by karaaage.

